<Author>Lovetravel70
<Content>Roach motel! We booked this hotel due to good reviews on more than one web site. Either those folks had a much different experience than us or they lied. This hotel is a complete dump. The elevators barely fit two people and two suitcases. The room had a roach in it and the shower was FULL of mold. It was just disgusting. My bf took pictures and went down to the desk to discuss with the staff. They tried to find another room, but it honestly took them two or three more rooms to find one that was acceptable. We turned it down and checked out the next morning. We spoke to the manager the next morning, showing him the photos. He said that his desk staff showed us 5 rooms (not true) and we declined them all. He said he didn't know where those photos were taken and refused to come up to the room to see for himself. He also said he would have to think about whether or not to refund us the two nights we would not be staying there (we paid in advance through the website), although we gave notice the previous night that we would not be staying there. As of now (a week later), we have not received the refund. 
