<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Perfect for a weeks break in Barca If you're a young couple or group without a great deal of money then Apartmento Gutenberg is worth considering!My girlfriend and I stayed there whilst doing the tourist thing in Barca and it is clean comfortable central and close to the places you want to be!Food is good, staff are very friendly and the rooms are spotless. We had a studio bedroom ensuite with kitchenette and balcony. The view is non existent as the hotel is down a side street, but if you're using it as a base only then it shouldn't be a problem.We are going back to Barca again this year and will be staying there again, I was very impressed with the hotel.The foyer is very nice and they have internet access for guests in the lobby, the photographs you may have see online don't do it justice either!I would give the hotel 10 out of 10!! Really enjoyed my stay!! 
